data.description: Well kept home, brand new AC, roof less than 15 years old.  Not a large space but with some personal touches it will be a great house. There’s room to expand in the backyard! House has , 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bath ,2 car garage. Great backyard and home is fully fenced.    *Pictures are before the tenant moved in* Tenant moved out, still working on minor repairs
